// Description: Basic version of UninaSoC that allows to work with axi transactions to and from slaves (ToBeUpdated)

// System architecture:
//                                                                                    ________
//                                                     __________                    |        |
//                                                    |          |                   |  Main  |
//                                                    |          |------------------>| Memory |
//                                                    |   Main   |                   |________|
//   ____________                                     |   Bus    |                    __________________
